source_classification rules:
- "resume_fact"  : Extract directly from candidate resume (name, skills, work history, education, location, qualifications)
- "generated"    : LLM writes professional prose based on the resume (cv_comments, expert_opinion, candidate_profile)
- "input_only"   : Recruiter-supplied or staffing-context values that are not extracted from the candidate resume (IDs, salary/availability inputs, presenter/contact metadata, role requirement fields)
